run this command : mkvirtualenv --python=/usr/bin/python3 mysite-virtualenv, an then,on same shell run :tele.py
on other shell run : eseguibile.sh


The program connects at the videocapture and analize the video,it i possibile to active/deactive the alarm with telegram.But before it is requirest create a bot python and insert in the file configurazione.txt the keys
in the file configurazione.txt insert the URL for connects at the videocapture in the browser

Install:

install in this dir:
yolov3.cfg
yolov3.weights
coco.names
